Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,学生总会辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还有明天开始就是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.30,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord2\c&H72C278&\3c&H302640&}捡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫有什么计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:53.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是出去购物之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长基本还是要打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:16:00.64,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord5\fs80\b1\pos(1339,946.6)}白银御行想出游
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比想象中更难调整出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,空闲时间还挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想干点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想干点什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 藤原书记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.08,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 藤原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:12.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然讨论过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是被保留了的旅行问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:25.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是腰斩还是实行全都由这个瞬间决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假种类繁多的活动中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:34.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是否男女混合举行与起跑冲刺紧密相连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:37.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,男女最初一起出去都是「接下来去哪里」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「那大家一起去吧」这样发展的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 如果起跑冲刺失败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就会增加男女混合的心理难度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,男生和男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,女生和女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样分组度过暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样失败的话就是灰色的暑假生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:03.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 没有没有……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}不会背木屐带断了的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}试胆大会也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}不会回到老家和青梅竹马再会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}穿越时间也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}异世界的召唤也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}不可能有夏日大冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}天体观测时看见流星许愿也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}暑假一起做作业也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}男女混合旅行也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}也不可能有被烟火声遮盖的情话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}合宿也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}混浴也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}兼职时恋爱也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord10\blur5}走光也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord10\blur5}人工呼吸也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord10\blur5}海边穿泳装也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord10\blur5}烧烤也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:07.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现实 这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和四宫去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:16.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果现在我问她们旅行的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:22.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀会长 那么久以前的事还翻出来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候也就是在兴头上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是随便说说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:34.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你真的觉得能去旅行还满怀期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.00,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不就会变成这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:44.47,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天夏天暑假暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行的话题不是你提出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那乐呵呵地跳什么舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:48.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原书记 果然暑假就要好好舒展一下对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:53.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 果然暑假就想做些平时做不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去旅行什么的最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:01.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然需要有时间从都市的喧嚣中解放出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我要去夏威夷玩一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.43,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:13.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是你闹着想大家一起去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛刚提出来 又擅自决定去夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.45,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,穿夏威夷衫去檀香山咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫 这是你的人吧 想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:24.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 旅行 很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:28.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜也理解暑假的起跑冲刺的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是辉夜和藤原的交往时间较长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:36.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明白不可能让藤原按照自己的想法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:40.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才需要「无」 注入祈祷的「无」的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.52,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,无
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完了一点也感觉不到四宫的霸气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 藤原书记要去旅行的话也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想要大家一起旅行本来就很难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:58.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也要一日游去哪里一起去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不带藤原同学去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:07.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说不是想和藤原同学而是想和我去玩是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶呀 真是 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,进退维谷了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没有藤原书记就没办法进行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:20.15,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,Aloha 檀香山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行一周回来后能干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:25.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原书记 海外是很好国内也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天还有各种活动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,高二的夏天就是天王山之战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:34.32,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,天王山：山崎之战中因当时战局而出现占领此山者便可获胜的状况。\N日语也从此出现‘决定天下的天王山’（天下分け目の天王山）此语，\N常藉以比喻运动与游戏的重要比赛。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有时间磨磨蹭蹭的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:36.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋太可恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你都去旅行了还有脸说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:43.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要把玩和学习分清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想要控制藤原同学是徒劳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就应该想想好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 本想这个夏天俘获四宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样都会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无计可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 还是想留下些回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:12.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是高一 会长已经高二了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:19.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明年就要备考不就不能玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只剩今年可以和会长好好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:28.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上 你是这样想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 夏天也不是必须要和女生玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:37.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以和兄弟一起犯蠢的度过夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:43.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 石上 夏末有一个大祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以请你吃章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.08,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧 一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚还说天王山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:54.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒啊 棉花糖 射击游戏 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:57.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和会长一起看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:20:59.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典据说是8月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把那天空出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:12.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 那几天是番茄节我在西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去旅游几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 欲望太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,无之心境崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你们难道要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:23.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:29.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会做出背着我其他人一起去夏日祭什么的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是正常的去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原前辈在番茄节不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩得那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,却不让我们去祭典也太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上君好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:50.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 冷血动物 刘海太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:56.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上君就应该被章鱼烧烫死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:02.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 石上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:09.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:14.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日战局 藤原以外全部胜利
