Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:15.14,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H030303&\an8\pos(276.8,486.4)\fs80}成\N功\N约\N好\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:15.14,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H030303&\an8\pos(193.6,481.6)\fs80}夏\N日\N祭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:15.14,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H030303&\an8\frz270\fs80\pos(233.6,740.8)})
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那当天19点去那里集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:24.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是男女搭配的暑假篇
